title: GoPro: Roberta Mancino Wingsuits Through Panama City Skyline
description:
GoPro Athlete, Roberta Mancino, splits two buildings with style as she takes flight in Panama City, Panama.

Video by: Noah Bahnson

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera

Music
William Ryan Fritch "Still"
